&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;b class="col_4"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-right: 25px"&gt;
	Grease formulators should now consider the possible benefits of this new cost effective, environmentally friendly, ashless antiwear additive. Commerical samples of Vanlube&lt;sup&gt;&lt;font size="2"&gt;&amp;reg;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; 972 are readily available for evaluation, and may be received by request at &lt;a href="mailto:petro@rtvanderbilt.com"&gt;Petro@RTVanderbilt.Com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
