            <title>Wireless condition monitoring for rotating equipment</title>
            <description>&lt;p id="eow-description"&gt;
	Ron Kittle, a senior product analyst for the Timken Company, talks about the StatusCheck wireless condition monitoring system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/motors/~4/GCH7UKbWzGA" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2011-01-06T15:59:36-06:00</a10:updated>
