            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:23532728-3a5c-47cb-a909-9d9d00ac2bad</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/motors/~3/jaRHjRCk4Uc/Relationship-voltage-current-motors</link>
