            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:06f5165a-6265-490e-9cb8-9d2900f16584</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/motors/~3/tbP1ItqYwH4/reliability-engineer-standards</link>
