            <title>ARC conducting survey on servo drive, motor purchasing</title>
            <description>&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial size=2&gt;ARC Advisory Group is conducting a survey on servo drive and motor purchasing trends for machinery. This survey is intended to assist respondents in benchmarking their drive and motor pricing relative to peers in and outside your industry. Power ranges and configuration of drives and motors are addressed for a wide range of industrial machinery which include in metal working, plastics, packaging, material handling, robotics, and others. 
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;Who Should Take the Survey?&lt;/B&gt;&lt;BR&gt;ARC encourages anyone involved in the sizing and/or selection of servo drive and motors particularly OEM machine builders and System Integrators to respond to this survey. &lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;Benefits of Taking the Survey&lt;/B&gt;&lt;BR&gt;All participants will receive a free copy of the results.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;ARC expects to learn more about pricing trends and configurations currently used by machine builders.&lt;/P&gt;
